##Configure the request mapping template.

{
    "version" : "2017-02-28",
    "operation" : "PutItem",
    "key": {
        "restaurantId": { "S": "$context.arguments.input.restaurantId"},
        "id": $util.dynamodb.toDynamoDBJson($util.autoId())
    },
    "attributeValues": {
    	"content": { "S": "$context.arguments.input.content" },
        "createdAt": { "S": "$context.arguments.input.createdAt" }
    }
}

##Configure the response mapping template.
$util.toJson($context.result)